# KPI Frame Tracker — Project Purpose

## What this system must do

- Track tasks measured in **frames**.
- Compute **deadline** for remaining work time.
- Track **KPI realtime** and **processing speed**.
- Predict **finish time** (estimated completion datetime).
- Manage workload and show risk warnings.
- **Auto-skip non-working time**:
  - Lunch break
  - After-work hours
  - Sundays (and future: holidays)

## Non-negotiables

- The **deadline calculation** must exclude:
  - 12:00–13:00 lunch
  - after 17:30 until next day 08:30
  - Sundays
- UI must update **realtime (every 1s)** for:
  - current time
  - remaining time
  - KPI status

